t_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn thua TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t khi ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng b\u1ecb n\u00e9m t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0o trong khu v\u1ef1c s\u00e2n \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eddi m\u01b0a, c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh, k\u00e9o chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n thua t\u1ea1i V-League 2018 l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 4.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nam Dinh bi phat vi nguoi ham mo nem phao sang vao san?\" title=\"Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t v\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 n\u00e9m ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng v\u00e0o s\u00e2n?\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/vua-thua-tran-nam-dinh-bi-phat-vi-cdv-dot-phao-sang.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><strong>Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t v\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 n\u00e9m ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng v\u00e0o s\u00e2n?</strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi v\u00ec ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong khu v\u1ef1c s\u00e2n. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n, 3 qu\u1ea3 ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e9m v\u00e0o trong khu v\u1ef1c s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea5t may l\u00e0 ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec1u r\u01a1i v\u00e0o ch\u1ed7 v\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y nguy hi\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c an ninh, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t. C\u0169ng trong m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, BTC s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eebng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t v\u00ec xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby, Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eebng ch\u1ecbu \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh vi \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean. Ngo\u00e0i ra, m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1c s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng phe v\u00e9 ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng khai ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc khu v\u1ef1c b\u00e1n v\u00e9 c\u1ee7a BTC.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC sau tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u tin kh\u00f4ng vui. Ngo\u00e0i nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam c\u0169ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng BXH V-League 2018, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a BTC, s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00f3n 11.000 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, \u00edt h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 21.000 (g\u1eb7p C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1) v\u00e0 17.000 (g\u1eb7p H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh 1-3 TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/14/nam-dinh-1-3-ho-chi-minh-1523714051.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-toshiya-miura-chi-ra-nguyen-nhan-giup-tp-ho-chi-minh-danh-bai-nam-dinh-291-184249.html\">HLV Toshiya Miura Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eadp b\u1eaby ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-nguyen-van-sy-lien-tuc-nhac-toi-tinh-than-cac-cau-thu-291-