a th\u1ea3i t\u1eeb Chelsea\" v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Giroud.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Conte dang cho Chelsea sa thai hinh anh\" title=\"Conte \u0111ang ch\u1edd Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/Conte-dang-cho-Chelsea-sa-thai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Conte \u0111ang ch\u1edd Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng thi\u1ebfu nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Conte</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa hi\u1ec7p, Conte \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n ng\u1ed3i \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho hi\u1ec7p hai. V\u00e0 c\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Dennis Wise c\u1ee7a Chelsea tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng cho th\u1ea5y Conte \u0111ang ch\u1edd b\u1ecb Abramovich g\u1eedi tr\u00e1t sa th\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cNh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Conte th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac. V\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m. T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ed5 v\u0169 Chelsea, th\u1eadt bu\u1ed3n khi ph\u1ea3i nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y Conte nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00ean khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t \u00f4ng \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Conte \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u00f4ng \u1ea5y b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y li\u00ean t\u1ee5c n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c v\u00ec c\u00e1c C\u0110V. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u1ee9 nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cChelsea li\u00ean t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n qua t\u1eebng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110i\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoc-dong-ha-guc-southampton-conte-noi-gi-172-184261.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/14/Conte-dang-cho-Chelsea-sa-thai-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoc-dong-ha-guc-southampton-conte-noi-gi-172-184261.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Southampton, Conte n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\n<span>T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 34, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, v\u00e0 HLV Conte ca ng\u1ee3i Giroud v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Conte n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Chelsea l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng Conte v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng vui v\u1ebb g\u00ec trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cM\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u, ni\u1ec1m \u0111am m\u00ea v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong hi\u1ec7p hai. Trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7p hai m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Southampton vs Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/giroud-tiet-lo-nguyen-nhan-giup-chelsea-nguoc-dong-southampton-172-184264.html\">Giroud ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap Chelsea ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng Southampton</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoc-dong-ha-guc-southampton-conte-noi-gi-172-184261.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Southampton, Conte n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-southampton-23-chelsea-172-184251.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn Southampton 2-3 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-southampton-23-chelsea-vong-34-premier-league-201718-326-184247.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Southampton 2-3 Chelsea (V\u00f2ng 34 Premier League 2017/18)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-southampton-vs-chelsea-tran-dau-vong-34-ngoai-hang-anh-201718-17