lay:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Salah ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed5 s\u00fang</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Salah kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ecbp h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City v\u00e0 m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Bournemouth \u1edf v\u00f2ng 34 Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ed3i gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n, Salah \u0111\u00e3 s\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Man City. V\u00e0 anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Bournemouth. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Alexander-Arnold \u0111\u1ec3 xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a The Cherries.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Mane v\u00e0 Firmino. \u201cC\u00e2y \u0111inh ba\u201d t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a The Kop ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 gi\u00fap cho The Kop x\u00e2y ch\u1eafc h\u01a1n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong top 4.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tiep tuc no sung, Salah lap ky luc o tran gap Bournemouth hinh anh\" title=\"Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed5 s\u00fang, Salah l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bournemouth h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/pha-luoi-bournemouth-salah-tiep-tuc-lap-them-ky-luc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Salah l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bournemouth</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>B\u00e0n th\u1eafng x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>V\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng v\u1eeba c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, Salah \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 30 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Premier League. Anh v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u00e0 Didier Drogba \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cVoi r\u1eebng\u201d t\u1eebng l\u1eadp n\u00ean c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c ghi 29 b\u00e0n v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2009/10 v\u00e0 gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0103n 3 qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt l\u00e2u, Salah \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c n\u00e0y v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Crystal Palace.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, Salah c\u00f2n x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c n\u1eefa khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n trong nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i Premier League. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n trong 22 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 21 b\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eafm gi\u1eef b\u1edfi Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Robin van Persie.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Bournemouth c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Salah \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 40 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn cho Liverpool. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch m\u00e0 Salah gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 sau 45 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/danh-sach-rut-gon-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-epl-salah-va-phan-con-lai-172-184262.html\" target=\"_blank\">Salah \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch r\u00fat g\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a PFA\u00a0cho gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Premier League</span> n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-liverpool-vs-bournemouth-tran-dau-vong-34-ngoai-hang-anh-201718-172-184256.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/ket-qua-liverpool-vs-bournemouth-tran-dau-vong-34-ngoai-hang-anh-201718.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-liverpool-vs-bournemouth-tran-dau-vong-34-ngoai-hang-anh-201718-172-184256.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Liverpool vs Bournemouth tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 34 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2017/18</span><br>\r\n<span>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Liverpool vs Bournemouth tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 34 gi\u1ea3i Premier League 2017/18 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Salah, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Jordan Henderson \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cSalah \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 m\u1ecdi k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Nh\u01b0ng Salah kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. C\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng di chuy\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3, Salah c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t kh\u1ecfe n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSalah l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn, hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Kane ghi b\u00e0n. Kane lu\u00f4n ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hat-trick b\u1edfi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. Aguero c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, Salah c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa\u201d.</em><strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nVideo t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Liverpool vs Bournemouth:<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_266512\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/04/15/highlight-liverpool-vs-bournemouth-vong-34-nha.mp4&autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Mohamed Salah:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/danh-sach-rut-gon-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-epl-salah-va-phan-con-lai-172-184262