b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111i sai h\u01b0\u1edbng, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0a t\u1eeb &lsquo;nh\u01b0ng&rsquo; v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3. R\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm khi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00edch c\u1ef1c m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng sau c\u00f9ng, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 che gi\u1ea5u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n. B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng \u01b0, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 19 CLB \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jose Mourinho bay to su bat cong vi bi truyen thong nguoc dai hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Jose Mourinho b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng v\u00ec b\u1ecb truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/mourin.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1eafng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c CLB trong Top 6, gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p m\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, v\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 c\u00fa l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3&rdquo; &ndash; HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng derby, Mourinho cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i cho t\u00f4i ni\u1ec1m h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0103n m\u1eebng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng cho \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 di\u1ec5n ra.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i th\u00e0 thua tr\u1eadn derby v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f2n h\u01a1n, th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea5y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1eeb gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, MU \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.&rdquo; &ndash; Jose Mourinho b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng d\u00e0nh cho CLB c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng West Brom, v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 Mourinho v\u00e0 MU tr\u00ean bongda24h<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-bac-bo-kha-nang-mua-them-tien-dao-172-184212.html\">Mourinho b\u00e1c b\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-len-ke-hoach-gia-han-voi-herrera-172-184187.html\">MU l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Herrera</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/rio-ferdinand-muon-mu-chieu-mo-sao-real-madrid-172-184095.html\">Rio Ferdinand mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-khuyen-rashford-va-martial-lam-quen-voi-ghe-du-bi-172-184188.html\">Mourinho khuy\u00ean Rashford v\u00e0 Martial l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-muon-tay-pogba-de-chieu-mo-ngoi-sao-nay-trong-he-toi-172-183972.html\">Mourinho m\u01b0\u1ee3n tay Pogba \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y trong h\u00e8 t\u1edbi?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-da-noi-gi-de-sanchez-lot-xac-tran-derby-172-183940.html\">Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 Sanchez l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Man City?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1189","checkdouble":"184278"},{"date":"04:18 15/04","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc Southampton","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/15/diem-nhan-sau-man-nguoc-dong-cua-chelsea-truoc-southampton.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.article