i m\u1ea1ch th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3i qua 1 tu\u1ea7n th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1edbi 3 tr\u1eadn thua li\u1ec3ng xi\u1ec3ng, nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng Man xanh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u00ecm s\u00e2u v\u00e0o kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng \u1edf chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Wembley. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1ch chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League \u0111\u00fang 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham vs Man City 1-3\" title=\"Tottenham vs Man City 1-3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/tottenham-13-man-city-mot-buoc-toi-thien-duong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Tottenham vs Man City 1-3 v\u00f2ng 34 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u 34, Man City s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh 2 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u1edf 6 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Tottenham l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Man City l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Pep-team c\u1ea7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1ch th\u1eafng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. V\u00e0 ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Gabriel Jesus. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean d\u00e2y c\u00f3t tinh th\u1ea7n cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, v\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y anh n\u00f3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-lieng-xieng-jesus-yeu-cau-man-city-guong-day-172-184176.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/thua-lieng-xieng-jesus-yeu-cau-man-city-guong-day.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-lieng-xieng-jesus-yeu-cau-man-city-guong-day-172-184176.html\">Thua li\u1ec3ng xi\u1ec3ng, Jesus y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Man City g\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1eady</span><br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u1ed9c c\u00f4 c\u1ea7u b\u1ea1i&rdquo; \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, Man City \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean d\u00e2y c\u00f3t tinh th\u1ea7n cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00f2ng 34 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. Man xanh v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111ang xu\u1ed1ng, v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Raheem Sterling li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c v\u1eabn ghi d\u1ea5u v\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9 3. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh khi\u1ebfn Hugo Lloris m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m (ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u1ea3 penalty n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n g\u1ee1 duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Spurs c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00e1 may m\u1eafn, khi Chris Eriksen v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Man xanh. V\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Wembley, nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u00edt \u1ecfi c\u1ee7a Tottenham c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ghi th\u00eam b\u00e0n. M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pochettino, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Harry Kane &ndash; c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111ang b\u1ecb c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0a con g\u00e1i ra th\u1ec1 th\u1ed1t \u0111\u00f2i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham vs Man City 1-3 Mot buoc toi thien duong hinh anh\" title=\"Tottenham vs Man City 1-3 M\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/Tottenham-vs-Man-City-1-3-Mot-buoc-toi-thien-duong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 do c\u00f4ng Eriksen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n Pep Guardiola n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu Man United b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 thua West Brom t\u1ed1i nay, c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi g\u00e3 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m \u1ed3n \u00e0o. Nh\u01b0ng k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra, vinh quang c\u0169ng \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb g\u00f5 c\u1eeda s\u00e2n Etihad.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Man xanh c\u00f2n \u0111ang mong Man \u0111\u1ecf gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, khi\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Raheem Sterling v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n m\u1eebng ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 22/4 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, khi h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Swansea t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 35 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 Man City \u0103n m\u1eebng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng v\u1ea1n C\u0110V nh\u00e0. M\u1ed9t k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u0111\u1eb9p cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, cho d\u00f9 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111i ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham vs Man City 1-3  Sterling ghi ban\" title=\"Tottenham vs Man City 1-3  Sterling ghi b\u00e0n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/ster.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 Tottenham vs Man City 1-3&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn Top 4 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Song song v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn ngai v\u00e0ng \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n k\u1ebft th\u00fac, m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua kh\u00e1c b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ea1i m\u1edf ra. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 gi\u1eefa Tottenham &ndash; CLB \u0111\u1ec3 thua v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, so v\u1edbi Chelsea &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Southampton, qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i &ldquo;ch\u1ec9&rdquo; c\u00f2n 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 5 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham, cho n\u00ean b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. \u0110\u00e0nh r\u1eb1ng, so phong \u0111\u1ed9 hay tinh th\u1ea7n, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1, G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u01b0 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Harry Kane v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho The Blues v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Antonio Conte \u0111ang r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch c\u00e0ng cao c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. H\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u1ed3i nh\u00e0 xem Champions League v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng m\u00f9a sau, b\u1edfi v\u1eady tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u0111ang r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cam ch\u1ecbu, gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn v\u00e0 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1ea1c quan nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Giroud ghi ban tran Southampton vs Chelsea\" title=\"Giroud ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Southampton vs Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/girouyd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Top 4 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ng\u00e3 ng\u0169</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Spurs, Hazard v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngay t\u1ea1i St Mary&rsquo;s. V\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Soton l\u00f3p ng\u00f3p v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, nh\u01b0ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Tottenham s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef l\u1ea5y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m g\u1ecdn trong t\u1ea7m tay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do cho th\u1ea5y gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean s\u1ee9c h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0103n m\u1eebng ngay t\u1eeb l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Tottenham vs Man City 1-3</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/11830508/013100\">Tottenham 1-3 Man City<br>\r\n</span><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_266523\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/15/tottenham-1-3-man-city.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-tottenham-vs-man-city-01h45-ngay-154-premier-league-201718-372-184253.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/ket-qua-tottenham-vs-man-city-tran-dau-vong-34-premier-league-201718.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-tottenham-vs-man-city-01h45-ngay-154-premier-league-201718-372-184253.html